      • hasAdvancedInformation

        public boolean hasAdvancedInformation()
        Returns:
        true if this type provider can provide more useful information (e.g. value range, nullability, etc.) on elements via getAdvancedInformationHint(PsiElement).

      • getAdvancedInformationHint

        public java.lang.String getAdvancedInformationHint(T element)
        Returns HTML string containing advanced type information hint (e.g. nullability, values range, etc.)
        Parameters:
        element - an element to provide information about
        Returns:
        an advanced information hint. Should return the same result as getInformationHint(PsiElement) if no additional information is available for given element.
        Throws:
        java.lang.UnsupportedOperationException - if this provider does not provide any advanced information (in this case hasAdvancedInformation() method must return false).
